启动动画，实在遭不住 3GB 内存了。</p>\n<p>尝试过用 iPad M1 替代手机，很多时候还是没有办法。</p>\n<p>然而 6GB 内存的 13 Pro Max 频率只有可怜的 238hz 。</p>\n<p>The display backlight flickers at 238.1 Hz (Likely utilizing PWM) .</p>\n<p><img alt=\"img\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://www.notebookcheck.net/fileadmin/_processed_/f/f/csm_NewFile0_2322db40fa.png\"/></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.notebookcheck.net/Apple-iPhone-13-Pro-Max-smartphone-review-Powerful-large-and-full-of-features.575239.0.html#toc-9\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.notebookcheck.net/Apple-iPhone-13-Pro-Max-smartphone-review-Powerful-large-and-full-of-features.575239.0.html#toc-9</a></p>\n<p>有坚持 XR/11 的用户么……手机日渐不行……该何去何从……</p>\n<p>哎……低频 PWM 调光……</p>\n", "last_modified": 1638320581, "replies": 115, "id": 819189}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3b5d/ca50/819_large.png?m=1633251402", "name": "watch", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3b5d/ca50/819_normal.png?m=1633251402", "title": " WATCH", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/watch", "topics": 708, "footer": "", "header": "<a href=\"/go/apple\">Apple</a> 公司设计的智能手表产品", "title_alternative": " WATCH", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3b5d/ca50/819_mini.png?m=1633251402", "stars": 342, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 819, "parent_node_name": "apple"}, "member": {"username": "windirt", "website": "http://www.cocoadew.com", "github": "windirt", "psn": "windirt", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/65d6/558f/33858_mini.png?m=1400119023", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/windirt", "tagline": "市场应用攻城狮转职码农ing", "twitter": "windirt", "created": 1360248109, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/65d6/558f/33858_mini.png?m=1400119023", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/65d6/558f/33858_mini.png?m=1400119023", "location": "深圳", "btc": "13HrgEpAwUZ1sX1k9FaK8QxFa2CL4JYenU", "id": 33858}, "last_reply_by": "badmarillo", "last_touched": 1638355545, "title":